> What level are you? As you go up on levels, your
> fights become longer and longer.

Ah, that could be it; my Dwarf's only 16th right now.
How long are we talking about? I was watching a group
kill Sand Giants in the Oasis Saturday night, they
were dropping them (to great cheers, I might add) in
under a minute each time.

Still, STA 95 is +20 over average (75).
